description: Package Description

Json and Xml Serializer for .NET projects

Support :
* Wpf, Windows Forms, Asp.Net
* Uwp (>=build 16299)
* Asp.Net Core, Xamarin (.Net Standard 2.0)
* etc.

* JsonO 
    * Methods 
        * ToJson: Object (object or dynamic) => Json 
        * FromJson: Json => Object (type or dynamic) 
        * ToXml: Object (object or dynamic) => Xml  
        * FromXml: Xml => Object (type or dynamic) 
    * Serialization Settings : Formatting, indentation, preserve circular reference, date format string (default: ISO), culture (default: InvariantCulture)
    * DefaultTypeResolver Settings: Naming Strategy (camel case, snake case or create a custom naming strategy), include Fields, include private/ non Public fields and properties, provider type to optimize object creation and getter/setter (dynamic by default, expression, reflection)
* Converters: default converters (object, ExpandoObject, enumerable, dictionary, primitive) or register / override a custom converter (with ConverterResolver)
* JsonTextReader and JsonTextWriter: allow to read and write Json
* Services: (for IoC containers)
   * JsonSerializationService (IJsonSerializationService)
